def smallest_number(numbers, k): 
    queue = deque(numbers)
    borrow = len(numbers) - k
    while borrow > 0:
        smallest = queue.popleft()
        if smallest > 0:
            borrow -= 1
            queue.append(smallest)
        else:
            borrow -= 1
            queue.append(0)
    return queue
